    "en": {
      "title": "Suspension of Ordinary Level Examination Answer Sheet Assessment Tasks",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the prevailing fuel shortage in the country. According to the Department of Examinations, the second phase of the Ordinary Level Examination has been suspended.",
        "Due to the fuel crisis situation, the evaluation work of the second phase of the GCE Ordinary Level Examination has been temporarily suspended.",
        "The first phase of the farewell evaluation process has been successfully completed. However the answer sheet evaluation work was carried out amidst various challenges.",
        "Further, the procedural examinations of the GCE Advanced Level Examination for the year 2021 are currently underway. The examinations are scheduled to be held till the 10th.",
        "GCE Advanced Level Examination Paper Assessment Tasks have reached the final stage. The GCE A / L for the year 2021 He said the high school exam results are scheduled to be released by the end of this month or within the first two weeks of August."
      ],
